Schema (12 fields):
  geo_id TEXT  FIPS or Census geographic identifier for the area
  name TEXT  Human-readable geographic area name
  year TEXT  ACS release year (e.g. 2024)
  dataset TEXT  ACS sub-dataset endpoint: acs1, acs1/subject, acs1/profile, 
