  table_id TEXT  ACS table identifier (e.g. B01001, S0101, DP02, CP05, S0201)
  variable_name TEXT  ACS variable code (e.g. B01001_001E)
  estimate TEXT  Numeric estimate value (cast to FLOAT in staging)
  margin_of_error TEXT  Margin of error associated with the estimate (variable 
ending in M)
  annotation TEXT  Annotation value if estimate has special meaning (e.g. (X) = 
not applicable)
  geo_level TEXT  Geography level queried (e.g. us, state, county, place)
  geo_fips TEXT  FIPS code for state or county component of geography
  popgroup TEXT  Population subgroup code for Selected Population Profiles (spp 
endpoint only)
